{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/javascript-como-fazer-capitalizeEveryWord/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"JS para impacientes"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"0ab8e3bf-4323-5ad1-88c4-9b17a885504c","excerpt":"Capitalizes the first letter of every word in a string. Use  to match the first character of each word and  to capitalize it. Acesse a Referência original","html":"<p>Capitalizes the first letter of every word in a string.</p>\n<p>Use <code class=\"language-text\">String.prototype.replace()</code> to match the first character of each word and <code class=\"language-text\">String.prototype.toUpperCase()</code> to capitalize it.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">capitalizeEveryWord</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">str</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">replace</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\">/\\b[a-z]/g</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token parameter\">char</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> char<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toUpperCase</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">capitalizeEveryWord</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'hello world!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 'Hello World!'</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/30-seconds/\">Acesse a Referência original</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"como usar o capitalizeEveryWord no javascript es6","date":"January 04, 2020","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/javascript-como-fazer-capitalizeEveryWord/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript-como-fazer-capitalize/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"como usar o capitalize no javascript es6"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript-como-fazer-call/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"como usar o call no javascript es6"}}}}}